        <body>       
                                

                <pb n="1"/>
            <p>Chicago July 6th 93.<lb/></p>
            <p>My dear Mr. Mora&#239;s.<lb/></p>
            <p>I wanted to tell<lb/> you myself how happy I<lb/> am over your prompt<lb/> recovery.  West as well as<lb/> East all those who love<lb/> you were deeply pained<lb/> and worried to hear of<lb/> your Sudden and dreadful<lb/> attack of illness and how<lb/> happy we all are of your<lb/> prompt improvement<lb/></p>
            <p>It seems to me a<lb/> true dream that you<lb/> will soon be in Chicago<lb/></p>
            
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>I know what a great<lb/> hebrew scholar you are.<lb/>  Now&#44; my great dear friend<lb/> do you not remember to<lb/> have read some where in<lb/> the bible.  That when some<lb/> noble man&#44; has devoted<lb/> his life and efforts to<lb/> all for a long life<lb/> time and reaches an<lb/> age&#44; when sickness is<lb/> often at his door and<lb/> his strength of will<lb/> far above his strength<lb/> of body&#44; that the time<lb/> has come when he<lb/> belongs to his children<lb/></p> 
            
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p><hi rend="underline">only</hi>.  He <hi rend="underline">must</hi> do exactly<lb/> as <hi rend="underline">they wish yes</hi> even<lb/> <hi rend="underline">obey</hi>.<lb/></p>
            <p>Now if this article<lb/> was not in your bible<lb/> I am sure you have not<lb/> the best edition.<lb/></p>
            <p>You must get<lb/> real strong in Minneapolis<lb/> then come to the<lb/> World&#39;s Fair&#44; where<lb/> your eyes and mind<lb/> will get feast never<lb/> tasted before&#44; never<lb/> again.<lb/></p>
            <p>This exposition is<lb/> so glorious&#44; so sublime<lb/> so beautiful&#44; that<lb/></p>
            
            <pb n="4"/>
            <p>is so awed in perfect<lb/> admiration.<lb/></p>
            <p>Give my love<lb/> to all your dear family<lb/> I will be so glad to<lb/> see you all.<lb/></p> 
            <p>With most<lb/> loving greetings<lb/></p> 
            <p>Your devoted<lb/> young friend<lb/> Hermine Jacoby<lb/></p>
            </body>
    </text>
